  }, "v4"), mdx("p", null, "Vua ra l\u1EC7nh cho th\u1EA7y t\u1EBF l\u1EC5 th\u01B0\u1EE3ng ph\u1EA9m Hinh-kia v\xE0 c\xE1c th\u1EA7y t\u1EBF l\u1EC5 c\u1EA5p d\u01B0\u1EDBi c\xF9ng nh\u1EEFng ng\u01B0\u1EDDi gi\u1EEF c\u1EEDa mang ra kh\u1ECFi \u0111\u1EC1n th\u1EDD CH\xDAA t\u1EA5t c\u1EA3 nh\u1EEFng th\u1EE9 \u0111\xE3 \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c l\xE0m cho Ba-anh, A-s\xEA-ra v\xE0 c\xE1c tinh t\xFA tr\xEAn tr\u1EDDi. R\u1ED3i Gi\xF4-xia \u0111\u1ED1t t\u1EA5t c\u1EA3 b\xEAn ngo\xE0i Gi\xEA-ru-sa-lem trong \u0111\u1ED3ng tr\u1ED1ng c\u1EE7a thung l\u0169ng K\xEDt-r\xF4n v\xE0 cho mang tro c\u1EE7a ch\xFAng \u0111\u1EBFn B\xEA-t\xEAn. "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v5"
