    "id": "v13"
  }, "v13"), mdx("p", null, "Vua Gi\xF4-xia c\u0169ng ph\xE1 h\u1EE7y nh\u1EEFng n\u01A1i th\u1EDD c\xFAng \u0111\u1ECBa ph\u01B0\u01A1ng \u1EDF ph\xEDa \u0111\xF4ng Gi\xEA-ru-sa-lem, v\u1EC1 ph\xEDa nam n\xFAi \xD4-liu. S\xF4-l\xF4-m\xF4n, vua \xCDt-ra-en, \u0111\xE3 x\xE2y nh\u1EEFng n\u01A1i \u0111\xF3. M\u1ED9t n\u01A1i d\xE0nh cho \xC1t-t\xF4-r\u1EBFt, n\u1EEF th\u1EA7n g\u1EDBm ghi\u1EBFc c\u1EE7a ng\u01B0\u1EDDi Xi-\u0111\xF4n, n\u01A1i kia d\xE0nh cho K\xEA-m\u1ED1t, th\u1EA7n \u0111\xE1ng gh\xEA t\u1EDFm c\u1EE7a M\xF4-\xE1p. M\u1ED9t n\u01A1i n\u1EEFa d\xE0nh cho M\xF4-l\xE9c, th\u1EA7n \u0111\xE1ng gh\xEA t\u1EDFm c\u1EE7a ng\u01B0\u1EDDi A-m\xF4n. "), mdx("h6", {
