  }, "v25"), mdx("p", null, "Tr\u01B0\u1EDBc v\xE0 sau Gi\xF4-xia kh\xF4ng c\xF3 vua n\xE0o gi\u1ED1ng nh\u01B0 \xF4ng. Vua h\u1EBFt l\xF2ng, h\u1EBFt linh h\u1ED3n, h\u1EBFt s\u1EE9c v\xE2ng theo CH\xDAA v\xE0 \u0111i theo m\u1ECDi l\u1EDDi gi\xE1o hu\u1EA5n c\u1EE7a M\xF4-se. "), mdx("h6", {
